{"word":"καρτέρησις","slug":"καρτέρησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καρτέρησις</b></el> <el>(καρτέρησις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:καρτερέω'><el>καρτερέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a bearing patiently, patience</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>patient endurance of</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}